headline: Nokia slumps after analyst predicts T-Mobile to ditch supplier
summary: Investing.com -- Nokia Corp ADR (NYSE:NOK) shares fell sharply Tuesday after an analyst predicted that T-Mobile US (NASDAQ:TMUS) Inc. could ditch the company for rival Ericsson for its 5G network equipment needs.
